Privacy Policy
Thank you for using the DiliCRM application. Below is our privacy policy regarding how we collect, use, and share your personal information:
Company Name: Dili Company
Registration and Login: The DiliCRM application is an internal tool and does not require user registration. The system automatically assigns account credentials for use.
Third-Party Services: Our application utilizes third-party services from Google Maps for map and location-related functionalities.
Data Storage Location: User data and information generated by the application will be stored in a secure database located on our internal servers. We have implemented measures to ensure the security and confidentiality of the data.
Data Retention Period: We will retain your personal information only for the time necessary to fulfill our contract with you or to comply with legal requirements. Once no longer needed, we will securely destroy or anonymize this information.
Information Sharing: We solemnly pledge that the DiliCRM application is for internal company use only. We will not sell, share, or disclose your personal information to any third parties.
Information Security: We employ various measures to safeguard the security of your personal information. We use encryption technologies and restrict access to information to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.
Contact Us: If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy policy, please contact us at the following:

Company Name: Dili Company
Email: jesse.li.yao@outlook.com

By using the DiliCRM application, you agree to and accept our privacy policy. We reserve the right to update or change the privacy policy at any time. Please check this page regularly for the latest information.
